data.description: Exceptional and practically new home awaits you in South Martin Branch, boasting an immaculate interior & top-notch features on a large cul-de-sac lot. Enjoy the benefits of lower taxes & energy efficiency, coupled with the convenience of nearby restaurants & medical facilities, as well as easy access to Hwy 287 & more. This exquisite, well-maintained home offers the convenience of all bedrooms located on the main floor, providing easy accessibility. Upstairs, a spacious game room awaits, perfect for children's entertainment and family gatherings. The large backyard is a paradise for kids, offering ample space for a future pool and endless playtime. Don't miss the opportunity to witness the charm of this home—it's a must-see for families seeking both comfort and entertainment options.
